
// The code connects to a PostgreSQL database using [pgsql.connect] and creates a new database. It concatenates the string "create database " with the database name from [.arguments] using [strings.concat], then executes this SQL command with [pgsql.execute], specifying the database name to use.
pgsql.connect:postgres
   strings.concat
      .:"create database "
      get-value:x:@.arguments/*/database
   pgsql.execute:x:-
      database:x:@.arguments/*/database
